        "subject": "LU-10337: Allow open of open orphans",
        "message": "LU-10337: Allow open of open orphans\n\nOpen by handle requires that we be able to open unlinked\nfiles.  This currently only works if the file is already\nopen on the same node.\n\nWhen an open file is unlinked, we put make it on orphan.\nThese files can be recognized by checking their open count\n(mod_count).  It's enough to just make opening these files\npossible, because the client cannot look them up to do an\nopen except when using a file handle.\n\nChange-Id: Id0693f6668c81890b2c7d9f26b689d6e7cd9d849\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <paf@cray.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
